Name: GET OUT!
About the game: Welcome to London, 1953. The Cold War is in full swing. You're a lone operative in dangerous territory. Can you uncover and complete the challenges awaiting you? A point-and-click escape room with secrets and consequences. Comes with mysterious toilet jokes and historically accurate propaganda. Features: • 8 timeless puzzles to beat • An ending to die for • Atmospheric original art and soundtrack
